{"word":"Treasure","slug":"treasure","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Treasure</b> A thing of highly estimated value.<br/> Money<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=42&verse=25'>Gen 42:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=42&verse=28'>Gen 42:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=42&verse=35'>Gen 42:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=43&verse=18'>Gen 43:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=43&verse=23'>Gen 43:23</a><br/> Precious stones<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=29&verse=8'>1Ch 29:8</a><br/> Jesus forbids the hoarding of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=6&verse=19'>Mat 6:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=19&verse=21'>Mat 19:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=12&verse=33'>Luk 12:33</a><br/> Hidden<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=44'>Mat 13:44</a><br/> Figurative:<br/> - Of the graces of the Spirit<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=21&verse=20'>Pro 21:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=33&verse=6'>Isa 33:6</a> <br/> - Of spiritual understanding<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=52'>Mat 13:52</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=2&verse=3'>Col 2:3</a> <br/> - Of the object of the affections<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=6&verse=21'>Mat 6:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=12&verse=34'>Luk 12:34</a> <br/> - Of spiritual calling<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=4&verse=7'>2Co 4:7</a> <br/> Gospel called<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=4&verse=7'>2Co 4:7</a><br/> Parable of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=44'>Mat 13:44</a>"}]}